description:
James recalls the early life of Jesus and His early ministry in Capernaum, describing how Jesus cast out demons and healed many people. The basis for this episode is Luke 4.

Scripture
Luke 4: 16-44, Matthew 4: 13-16, Matthew 8: 14-17, Mark 1: 21-39

Director: Phil Smith
Stars: Andy Axewell
